dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Ancillary maps: Population -- Economic activity. "Boundary representation is not necessarily authoritative." "59205 4-69." Showing national and provincial boundaries and capitals, roads, railways, airfields, and ports. Includes ancillary maps of population and economic activity in Nile Valley, Sinai, and Gaza.
